var dt = new Date();
var y = dt.getFullYear();
var m = dt.getMonth();
m = m + 1;//since js represent month between 0 and 11, so add one to adjust.
var d = dt.getDate();

getData() returns the day of the month, while getDay() returns the day of the week.
getMonth() returns the number between 0 and 11. So, need adjustment.